sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (Tool)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Section 3.22, Table 201 - Reusable State: Charging
    Note over CP,CS: OCPP 1.6J (page 174/176)
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Authorized state (Table 200, document page 173-174)

    CP->>CS: StatusNotification.req
    Note right of CP: status = Preparing<br/>connectorId = <Configured ConnectorId>
    CS-->>CP: StatusNotification.conf

    CP->>CS: StartTransaction.req
    Note right of CP: idTag = <Configured Valid IdTag><br/>connectorId = <Configured ConnectorId>
    CS-->>CP: StartTransaction.conf
    Note over CS: Validation: idTagInfo.status should be Accepted

    CP->>CS: StatusNotification.req
    Note right of CP: status = Charging<br/>connectorId = <Configured ConnectorId>
    CS-->>CP: StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP,CS: State is Charging
